419	devforum	4186615	Npc Follow Player Script Not Workng	https://devforum.roblox.com/t/4186615	Scripting	The script attempts to use game.Players.LocalPlayer within a server-side Script located inside an NPC in the Workspace, resulting in a nil value and preventing the follow logic from executing.	Replace the LocalPlayer reference with server-side logic to identify players, such as iterating through game.Players:GetPlayers() to find the nearest character or using spatial queries. Alternatively, the RunContext of the script can be changed to Client, though server-side logic is standard for NPC behavior.	t	beginner	{RunService.Heartbeat,Players.LocalPlayer,Humanoid:MoveTo,IsPointInRegion3,RunContext}	{}	t	Identify the usage of 'LocalPlayer' in non-LocalScript contexts and recommend iterating through the Players service or using distance/spatial checks.	90	2	3	2025-12-26 19:16:34.159	2026-01-08 17:13:19.37658	{"views": 90, "content": " Hi, I’m trying to make a npc that follows the player while they’re in a zone (part), but the script isn’t working. There’s no errors in the output, and the script is located in the npc. Pls pls help Here’s the code: \\n  local zonePart = game.Workspace.Zone1\\nlocal npc = script.Parent  \\nlocal humanoid = npc:FindFirstChildOfClass(\\"Humanoid\\")  \\nlocal followSpeed = 16  \\n\\nlocal function isPlayerInZone(player)\\n   local character = player.Character\\n   if character then\\n       local humanoidRootPart = character:FindFirstChild(\\"HumanoidRootPart\\")\\n       if humanoidRootPart then\\n           return zonePart:IsPointInRegion3(humanoidRootPart.Position)\\n       end\\n   end\\n   return false\\nend\\n\\nlocal function followPlayer(player)\\n   local character = player.Character\\n   local humanoidRootPart = character:FindFirstChild(\\"HumanoidRootPart\\")\\n   if humanoidRootPart then\\n       local direction = (humanoidRootPart.Position - npc.HumanoidRootPart.Position).unit\\n       humanoid:MoveTo(npc.HumanoidRootPart.Position + direction * followSpeed)\\n   end\\nend\\n\\ngame:GetService(\\"RunService\\").Heartbeat:Connect(function()\\n   local player = game.Players.LocalPlayer \\n   if player and isPlayerInZone(player) then\\n       followPlayer(player)\\n   end\\nend)\\n\\nzonePart.Touched:Connect(function(hit)\\n   local character = hit.Parent\\n   local player = game.Players:GetPlayerFromCharacter(character)\\n   \\n   if player then\\n       if isPlayerInZone(player) then\\n           followPlayer(player)\\n       else\\n           humanoid:MoveTo(npc.Position)  \\n       end\\n   end\\nend)  ", "upvotes": 2, "category": "scripting-support", "comments": 3, "created_at": "2025-12-26T19:16:34.159Z"}
