d\\n\\t\\t\\t\\tend\\n\\t\\t\\t\\tCursor = Data.nextPageCursor or \\"\\"\\n\\t\\t\\telse\\n\\t\\t\\t\\tCursor = \\"\\"\\n\\t\\t\\tend\\n\\t\\telse\\n\\t\\t\\tif string.find(Result, \\"403\\") then\\n\\t\\t\\t\\twarn(\\"The player with the user id: \\" .. UserId .. \\" has a private inventory!\\")\\n\\t\\t\\t\\treturn Ids\\n\\t\\t\\tend\\n\\t\\t\\twarn(\\"Failed to get inventory: \\" .. tostring(Result))\\n\\t\\t\\tCursor = \\"\\"\\n\\t\\tend\\n\\tuntil Cursor == \\"\\"\\n\\n\\treturn Ids\\nend\\n  \\n Any other proxy I should use? Or maybe a way with Players or Marketplace service? ", "upvotes": 0, "category": "scripting-support", "comments": 10, "created_at": "2025-12-26T14:27:42.698Z"}
