st the frame. I need it so that when you click the frame, nothing happens. Shall I make the frame a button as well, and disable the auto button color? In my main game, the frame is actually a scrolling frame, so I can’t do that. So just put a button behind the scrolling frame to absorb the clicks from the  BackgroundClickDetectorTextButton ? \\n  -- This is an example Lua code block\\n  \\n Please do not ask people to write entire scripts or design entire systems for you. If you can’t answer the three questions above, you should probably pick a different category. \\n Thanks in advance everyone! ", "upvotes": 3, "category": "scripting-support", "comments": 7, "created_at": "2026-01-04T01:42:33.345Z"}
