des things. That does not fix the memory issue. \\n Also, I’m not asking for an entire system or script. I just want to know how to approach this, then I can design and script everything myself. ", "upvotes": 0, "category": "scripting-support", "comments": 2, "created_at": "2026-01-03T16:07:52.605Z"}
