aterial, scale, …)\\nGeneration of Areas (parks, fields, pitches, …)\\n Ro scale  compatibility\\nHistory - previously used coordinates save\\n\\nGet the plugin here:  WorldLoader  \\nAlso available on  Github  \\nAll data is provided by  Openstreetmaps  \\nAny problems with the plugin, bugs, feeback or help needed? Join my  Discord Server  \\n\\n\\nG…\\n   \\n \\n\\n I’ve tried heightmaps as well, but I’m getting similar inaccurate results. \\n If anyone has advice or a workflow that produces more accurate terrain around rail networks, I’d really appreciate the help! ", "upvotes": 0, "category": "building-support", "comments": 5, "created_at": "2025-11-22T20:49:26.145Z"}
