racter[tool.Name]:IsA(\\"Tool\\") then\\n\\t\\txpDeb = true\\n\\t\\t-- created tag(Player who holds the tool)\\n\\t\\tlocal tag = Instance.new(\\"ObjectValue\\")\\n\\t\\ttag.Name = plr.Name\\n\\t\\ttag.Value = plr\\n\\t\\ttag.Parent = hit.Parent\\n\\t\\t-- \\n\\t\\txp.Value = xp.Value + xpGiver.Value --ignore\\n\\t\\tprint(plr.Name..\\"Killed \\"..hit.Parent.Name..\\", Recieved\\".. xpGiver.Value..\\"XP\\")  --ignore\\n\\t\\ttask.wait() \\n\\tend\\n\\ttask.wait() --ignore\\n\\txpDeb = false --ignore\\nend)\\n  \\n I will be grateful if someone tells me what is happening so I can get it fixed ", "upvotes": 4, "category": "scripting-support", "comments": 4, "created_at": "2025-12-26T13:28:50.304Z"}
